### 9. 自动配置类实例化和 Bean 注册

```java
/**
 * 实例化配置类并注册 Bean
 */
private void instantiateAndRegisterBeans(String configClassName) {
    try {
        // 1. 实例化配置类
        Class<?> configClass = Class.forName(configClassName);
        Object configInstance = configClass.newInstance();

        // 2. 解析@Bean 方法
        Method[] methods = configClass.getDeclaredMethods();
        for (Method method : methods) {
            if (method.isAnnotationPresent(Bean.class)) {
                // 3. 调用@Bean 方法获取 Bean 实例
                Object bean = method.invoke(configInstance);

                // 4. 注册到容器
                String beanName = method.getName();
                beanFactory.registerBean(beanName, bean);
            }
        }
    } catch (Exception e) {
        System.out.println("Failed to instantiate config: " + configClassName);
    }
}
```

